      • newPwdPolicy

        public Pwd_Policy newPwdPolicy​(com.yardi.shared.QSECOFR.EditPwdPolicyRequest editPwdPolicyRequest)
        Construct a new Pwd_Policy request by mapping EditPwdPolicyRequest to Pwd_Policy. Several columns in PWD_POLICY may contain null. To map these correctly from EditPwdPolicyRequest test for a String with a value of "null". If the field from EditPwdPolicyRequest is "null" set the corresponding field in Pwd_Policy to null. Otherwise, the corresponding field in Pwd_policy is mapped to String or Short
